com.skratchdot.riff.wav.impl

Class ChunkSamplerImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • EObjectImpl
      • com.skratchdot.riff.wav.impl.ChunkImpl
        • com.skratchdot.riff.wav.impl.ChunkSamplerImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Chunk, ChunkSampler

    public class ChunkSamplerImpl
extends ChunkImpl
implements ChunkSampler
    An implementation of the model object 'Chunk Sampler'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Manufacturer
    • Product
    • Sample Period
    • Midi Unity Note
    • Midi Pitch Fraction
    • Smpte Format
    • Smpte Offset
    • Number Of Sample Loops
    • Sampler Data Size
    • Sample Loops
    • Sampler Data
